      • toArguments

        public ArgumentsSupplier toArguments(Command cmd)
        Parses the given command according to the properties described by this container. This returns an ArgumentsSupplier that will supply the arguments in cmd in the same order as described by this container.
        Parameters:
        cmd - Command to parse
        Returns:
        The ArgumentsSupplier corresponding to the given command and this container.
